\left|\frac{sin x}{x^{n+1}}\right|\leq \frac{1}{x^{n+1}}
\int_{1}^{\infty}\left|\frac{\sin x}{x^{n+1}}\right| dx\leq \int_{1}^{\infty}\frac{dx}{x^{n+1}}=\lim_{t\to\infty}\left(\frac{x^{-n}}{-n}\right)\Big|_{1}^t=\frac{1}{n}.
